item.description:
@WRX wrote:

You can’t edit the folder as a co-owner, ask the owner to program a command for creating objects in game.

for ::setobject, you using mopar client?
If so, it tells you on there…

Ps. If you want something personal on a server you ask the administrator/owner of the server. We cannot help.
